    "body": "I feel like paths should be relative, similar to how Python packages work.\r\n\r\nSo I would propose that `ballot.vy` look like:\r\n```python\r\nimport ..interfaces.ballot_interface as BallotInterface \r\nimplements: BallotInterface\r\n```\r\n\r\nOtherwise, if I compile from another directory, how do I know where things are located?\r\n\r\n@charles-cooper @jacqueswww thoughts?",
